  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Operations Supervisor (3PL Logistics MNC)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a well-established MNC, market leader in the Logistics industry. They are looking for a Warehouse Supervisor to assist their team for the next phrase of their business. They are located in the east.</p><p><strong>This Warehouse Supervisor would be responsible for:</strong></p><ul><li>Lead and manage a team of operations staff</li><li>Oversee inventory control and stock accuracy</li><li>Ensure smooth daily operations and team coordination</li><li>Supervise order picking, packing, and on-time delivery</li><li>Meet daily targets within required lead times</li><li>Enforce QHSE compliance in all processes</li><li>Maintain warehouse cleanliness and organization</li><li>Handle warehouse activities including receiving, sorting, packing, and container handling</li><li>Operate lifting equipment safely (if authorized)</li><li>Conduct regular cycle counts and annual stock takes</li><li>Assist Executive with daily tasks and ad-hoc duties</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma/ Bachelor's degree in Logistics or relevant studies.</li><li>Min 3 years of supervisory experience in 3PL warehouse.</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p>Email: <strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.<br />EA License No. 19C9682<br />EA Reg. No. R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
